Texts.Eng: A block of weird glass doesn't make for the comfiest chair...

Texts.Eng: A cleanly cut chair made from refractive glass.
Texts.Por: Uma cadeira feita de vidro refractário.

This chair manages to constantly catch the light shining within it.
